<section2 id="sExclExcl">
	<secTitle>Exclamations</secTitle>
<p contentType="ctComparativeIntro"><content>Exclamations typically consist of a particular word, such as </content><langData>how</langData><content> in English, followed by an adjective phrase and usually punctuated with an exclamation point.  English examples include: </content>
   <langData>How awful for you!</langData><content> and </content><langData>How nice!</langData><content> and </content><langData>How wonderful that your family could come!</langData>
</p>
   <p contentType="ctPracticalIntro"><content>Exclamations typically consist of a particular word followed by an adjective phrase and usually punctuated with an exclamation point.</content></p>  
<p show="swExclMNo"><langName/><content> does not have a special word which marks exclamations of this type, so they are no different than the interjections consisting of adjectives in the previous section.</content></p>
   <p show="swExclMYes"><langName/> <content> has one or more special words which signal an exclamation which occur </content>
      <text show="swExclMBefore"><content>before</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMAfter"><content>after</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMBoth"><content>on both sides of</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMEither"><content>on either side of</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMBeforeOrBoth"><content>before or on both sides of</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMAfterOrBoth"><content>after or on both sides of</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMEitherOrBoth"><content>on either side or on both sides of</content></text>
      <text show="swExclMNotOther"><content> the adjective phrase.  </content></text>
      <text show="swExclMOtherOnly"><content>___</content><contentCheckBoxOther contentLoc="excl/exclMOther"/><content>.    </content></text>
      <text show="swExclMPosAndOther"><content> the adjective phrase and it may also occur ___</content><contentCheckBoxOther contentLoc="excl/exclMOther"/><content>.  </content></text>
      
   <content>These exclamation marker words are:</content></p>
<example show="swExclMYes"><table border="1">
